{"tid":2272773,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【延任議會】主持立法會大會   梁君彥、李慧琼關注美國大選","createTime":"2020-11-05T09:17:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T09:20:16.000Z","uid":134093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"217c88a711148f89e736926123739cc1afc26b6b","tid":2272773,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T09:17:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7PvaEAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7PvaEAi.jpg&h=b6dc6001&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【延任議會】主持立法會大會   梁君彥、李慧琼關注美國大選<br />\n<br />\n立法會今（5 日）早 9 時續會，大會已完成《2019 年運貨貨櫃（安全）（修訂）條例草案》二讀辯論，進入全體委員會階段。另一邊廂，美國大選選情緊張，無論立法會主席梁君彥、代主席李慧琼，主持會議時都一心二用，在電腦屏幕打開美國選情的實時追蹤。<br />\n<br />\n立法會今日議程尚有三條由議員提出的決議案，隨後會處理譴責議員議案，首先是譴責民建聯周浩鼎議案，之後是譴責民主黨許智峯的議案。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3617299205022340/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3617299205022340%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4MRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=57f017af\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3617299205022340/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"3c0bc2ed39b35688ef3dfd8e9aba4b11ef038373","tid":2272773,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T09:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43470140d13675842d3222813e3c9287e5f4f441","tid":2272773,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T09:20:16.000Z","msg":"人大習近平都仲未關注<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又搞港獨"}]}